nodes.code:
let reqUrl = this.base_url + "/Confirm"
meta reqUrl = $reqUrl

let request = {
    "url": $reqUrl,
    "reqBody": {
        "Token": this.access_token,
        "PartnerCode": this.partner_code,
        "PartnerRefNo": this.transRef,
        "BillerCode": this.billerCode,
        "TransactionAmount": this.transactionAmount,
        "Detail": this.detail,
    }
}
root.request = $request

meta startTime2c2p = timestamp_unix()
meta requestBody2c2p = $request
meta action2c2p = this.action
nodes.desc: เตรียมข้อมูลเรียก Biller List
nodes.name: Prepare for Confirm

nodes.code:
hp_http:
    url: ${! meta("reqUrl") }
    verb: POST
    
    headers:
        Content-Type: "application/json"
    
    input: |
        root = this.request.reqBody
    
    result_mode: "merge"
    
    output: |
        root = {}
        root.result = this.or({})
    
    timeout: 45s
    
    retries: 0
    
    tls:
        enabled: true
        skip_cert_verify: true
        enable_renegotiation: true

nodes.code:
hp_function:
  name: "call_http_2c2p_auth"
  input: |
    root = this
  result_mode: "merge"
  output: |
    root = this.or({"error":"Call Authentication Failure"})

  processors:
    - label: "maping"
      mapping: |
        root = this.body.string()

    - hp_http:
        url: "${! meta(\"_reqUrl_2c2p\") }"
        verb: POST

        headers:
          Content-Type: text/plain
          Authorization: "${! meta(\"_basic_auth_2c2p\") }"

        result_mode: "new"

        output: |
          root = {}
          root.tokenData = this

        timeout: 45s
    
        retries: 0
    
        tls:
            enabled: true
            skip_cert_verify: true
            enable_renegotiation: true
